          {% elif (content.slug is string_startingwith "fr/") or (content.slug =="fr")  %}
               &lt;h5&gt; &lt;a   class="entry-title text-center" href="{{ request.path }}/{{ row.hs_path }}"&gt; {{ row.name_fr }} &lt;/a&gt; &lt;/h5&gt;
          {% elif (content.slug is string_startingwith "pol/") or (content.slug =="pol")  %}
               &lt;h5&gt; &lt;a   class="entry-title text-center" href="{{ request.path }}/{{ row.hs_path }}"&gt; {{ row.name_pol }} &lt;/a&gt; &lt;/h5&gt;
          {% elif (content.slug is string_startingwith "ru/") or (content.slug =="ru")  %}
              &lt;h5&gt; &lt;a   class="entry-title text-center" href="{{ request.path }}/{{ row.hs_path }}"&gt; {{ row.name_ru }} &lt;/a&gt; &lt;/h5&gt;
          {% else %}
                 &lt;h5&gt; &lt;a   class="entry-title text-center" href=" {{ request.path }}/{{ row.hs_path }}"&gt; {{ row.name }} &lt;/a&gt; &lt;/h5&gt;
          {% endif %} vorrei que quando sente url /en vada a prendre il name nel secondo DB per restituirmi il page path in inglese.come posso fare?

Here's what I came up with:
```{% set queryparam = "" %}
&lt;!-- Type only filter--&gt;
{% if request.query_dict.type in ["1", "2", "3", "4"] and request.query_dict.listing_bedrooms == "show-all" and request.query_dict.listing_price == "show-all" %}
    {% set queryparam = queryparam ~ "&amp;type="~request.query_dict.type|urlencode %}
{% endif %}
&lt;!-- Price only filter--&gt;
{% if request.query_dict.type == "show-all" and request.query_dict.listing_bedrooms == "show-all"  and request.query_dict.listing_price != "show-all" %}
    {% set queryparam = queryparam ~ "&amp;listing_price="~request.query_dict.listing_price|urlencode %}
{% endif %}
&lt;!-- Bedrooms only filter--&gt;
{% if request.query_dict.type == "show-all" and request.query_dict.listing_bedrooms != "show-all"  and request.query_dict.listing_price == "show-all" %}
    {% set queryparam = queryparam ~ "&amp;listing_bedrooms="~request.query_dict.listing_bedrooms|urlencode %}
{% endif %}

&lt;!-- Type and Price filters--&gt;
{% if request.query_dict.type in ["1", "2", "3", "4"] and request.query_dict.listing_bedrooms == "show-all"  and request.query_dict.listing_price != "show-all" %}
    {% set queryparam = queryparam~"&amp;type="~request.query_dict.type|urlencode~"&amp;listing_price="~request.query_dict.listing_price|urlencode %}
{% endif %}
&lt;!-- Type and Bedrooms filters--&gt;
{% if request.query_dict.type in ["1", "2", "3", "4"] and request.query_dict.listing_bedrooms != "show-all"  and request.query_dict.listing_price == "show-all" %}
    {% set queryparam = queryparam~"&amp;type="~request.query_dict.type|urlencode~"&amp;listing_bedrooms="~request.query_dict.listing_bedrooms|urlencode %}
{% endif %}
&lt;!-- Price and Bedrooms filters--&gt;
{% if request.query_dict.type == "show-all" and request.query_dict.listing_bedrooms != "show-all"  and request.query_dict.listing_price != "show-all" %}
    {% set queryparam = queryparam~"&amp;listing_price="~request.query_dict.listing_price|urlencode~"&amp;listing_bedrooms="~request.query_dict.listing_bedrooms|urlencode %}
{% endif %}

&lt;!-- All filters--&gt;
{% if request.query_dict.type in ["1", "2", "3", "4"] and request.query_dict.listing_bedrooms != "show-all"  and request.query_dict.listing_price != "show-all" %}
    {% set queryparam = queryparam~"&amp;type="~request.query_dict.type|urlencode~"&amp;listing_bedrooms="~request.query_dict.listing_bedrooms|urlencode~"&amp;listing_price="~request.query_dict.listing_price|urlencode %}
{% endif %}```
